flowchart TD
    A[Request Start] --> CheckSetting{forceResponsesEndpoint?}

    CheckSetting -- false --> ChatPipeline[Chat/Completions API]
    CheckSetting -- true --> CheckModel{modelInfo.mode?}

    CheckModel -- chat --> ChatPipeline
    CheckModel -- responses --> ResponsesPipeline[Responses API]

    ChatPipeline -- success --> Done[Return Response]
    ChatPipeline -- failure --> Error[Error State]

    ResponsesPipeline -- success --> Done
    ResponsesPipeline -- failure --> CheckFallback{allowChatCompletionsFallback?}

    CheckFallback -- true --> ChatPipeline
    CheckFallback -- false --> Error